channel.title: [Paying PayPal] Webclient Error [$$]
channel.description:
So I made a .jar and it works perfectly fine. I can download the .jar and play my server off of it. The problem comes when I run it in an HTML page it doesn't work. It says "Requesting Title Screen" than after 1-2 seconds "Connection Error - retrying in..."
If someone can give me a fix for this I will pay them $3 over Paypal. Seems like a fair deal to me since it should be pretty easy. I have teamviewer if that's how you want to fix it otherwise, please post a tutorial for the fix.
